Florida Public Utilities Cosaid its board declared a three-for-two stock split on itscommon stock.    It said holders of record April 15 will receive oneadditional share May one for each two shares held.    The company also said it raised the dividend on its commonstock by two cts to 33 cts a share on a pre-split basis.    The dividend is payable April one to holders of recordMarch 18. Reuter&#3;